## 📌 TASK 12 — Model Persistence

### What to Save

| Artifact | Format | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| Trained classification model | `.pkl` / `.joblib` | Role prediction at inference time |
| TF-IDF vectorizer | `.pkl` / `.joblib` | Transform new resumes to features |
| Label encoder | `.pkl` / `.joblib` | Map predictions back to role names |
| Scoring weights | [.json](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/careerforge%202-%20Copy/package.json) | Resume scoring dimension weights |
| Risk thresholds | [.json](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/careerforge%202-%20Copy/package.json) | Low/Medium/High cutoff values |
| Skill database | [.json](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/careerforge%202-%20Copy/package.json) | Expanded AI-learned skill map |
| Performance report | [.json](file:///c:/Users/Shuddhodhan/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/careerforge%202-%20Copy/package.json) | All evaluation metrics for audit |

### Model Versioning

| Field | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `model_version` | Incrementing version number |
| `trained_date` | Timestamp of training |
| `dataset_hash` | Hash of training data for reproducibility |
| `performance_metrics` | Accuracy, F1, etc. at time of training |

